{{#> base-layout}}
<h2>Task Overdue Reminder</h2>

<div class="urgent">
    <h3>⚠️ {{name}}</h3>
    <p><strong>Due Date:</strong> {{formatDate due_date}}</p>
    <p><strong>Overdue by:</strong> {{overdue_duration}}</p>
</div>

<p>Hello {{assigned_user_name}},</p>

<p>This is a reminder that the following task is now overdue:</p>

<ul>
    <li><strong>Task:</strong> {{name}}</li>
    <li><strong>Opportunity:</strong> {{opportunity_name}}</li>
    <li><strong>Client:</strong> {{client_name}}</li>
    <li><strong>Service:</strong> {{service_name}}</li>
    <li><strong>Original Due Date:</strong> {{formatDate due_date}}</li>
    <li><strong>Current Status:</strong> {{status}}</li>
    {{#if description}}
    <li><strong>Description:</strong> {{description}}</li>
    {{/if}}
</ul>

<p><strong>Please complete this task as soon as possible to avoid further delays.</strong></p>

<a href="{{app_url}}/tasks/{{id}}" class="button">Complete Task Now</a>

<p>If you need assistance or have encountered any blockers, please reach out to your supervisor immediately.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
WondrlabApp Team</p>
{{/base-layout}}
